aysinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2644130/extras/01ae9a5421fe7a706d7c1fad2a961d71.poster.avif?t=1726039821\" width=616 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2644130/extras/01ae9a5421fe7a706d7c1fad2a961d71.webm?t=1726039821\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2644130/extras/241bd47e2ea8116778bbbfdc07c8fc83.apng?t=1726039821\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2644130/extras/241bd47e2ea8116778bbbfdc07c8fc83.poster.avif?t=1726039821\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=350 /></picture></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2644130/extras/81d4d9484514e8cc8a5b2181817fc03d.apng?t=1726039821\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2644130/extras/81d4d9484514e8cc8a5b2181817fc03d.poster.avif?t=1726039821\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=350 /></picture></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2644130/extras/ba5684e80faf598ae896e834e58cec78.webp?t=1726039821\" width=616 height=35 /></span><br>Embracing the 'easy-to-learn, hard-to-master' paradigm, the game offers a steadily increasing challenge, growing more formidable with each passing minute. Stay on your toes and avoid getting caught by the pursuing women.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2644130/extras/03b934ba798b95d3fbafb1523b698d4e.webp?t=1726039821\" width=616 height=35 /></span><br>The story unfolds through a collection of light-hearted, humorous, and brief videos that offer a deeper insight into the background of each playable map and unraveling the player's path, helping you comprehend the journey you've undertaken to elude your unhinged admirers who are so deeply in love with you. Keep your eyes peeled; you might just stumble upon a hidden ending. Who can predict what awaits?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2644130/extras/5f5c98f192747d7abc337e857e325c69.apng?t=1726039821\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2644130/extras/5f5c98f192747d7abc337e857e325c69.poster.avif?t=1726039821\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=240 /></picture></span>",
